OL,3,CHarry and Meghan join Aboriginal
OL,4,Cwalking tour in Australia
OL,6,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex have
OL,7,Fjoined an Aboriginal walking tour in
OL,8,FMelbourne.
OL,10,FHarry and Meghan took part in the Scar
OL,11,FTree Walk, which connects traditional
OL,12,Fand contemporary Aboriginal cultures
OL,13,Fand the histories of the local Kulin
OL,14,FPeoples on Thursday morning.
OL,16,FA scar tree, also known as a canoe
OL,17,Ftree or shield tree, has had bark
OL,18,Fremoved by Aboriginal Australians for
OL,19,Fthe creation of bark canoes, shelters,
OL,20,Fweapons, tools, traps and containers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
