OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776301390
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan join Aboriginal
OL,4,Cwalking tour in Australia
OL,6,FScar trees may also be created as a
OL,7,Fform of artistic and spiritual
OL,8,Fexpression by some Aboriginal peoples,
OL,9,Fto mark places of significance such as
OL,10,Fburial sites, and provide a link to
OL,11,F60,000 years of continuous culture.
OL,13,FThe walk is led by local Indigenous
OL,14,Fguides, beginning at the Koorie
OL,15,FHeritage Trust in Melbourne's
OL,16,FFederation Square. Koorie is a term
OL,17,Fwhich refers to Indigenous people from
OL,18,FVictoria and parts of New South Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
