OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776301390
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan join Aboriginal
OL,4,Cwalking tour in Australia
OL,6,FThe walk follows the Birrarung (Yarra
OL,7,FRiver) and meanders through Birrarung
OL,8,FWilam (river camp) Aboriginal art
OL,9,Fpieces and contemporary installations.
OL,11,FIt continues over William Barak
OL,12,FBridge, named after an elder of the
OL,13,FWurundjeri-willam clan, which crosses
OL,14,FBatman Avenue, to enter a traditional
OL,15,FKulin Nation meeting place which is
OL,16,Fthousands of years old.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
