PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776301390
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan join Aboriginal
OL,4,Cwalking tour in Australia
OL,6,FThe meeting place of the Wurundjeri
OL,7,Fpeople is now the site of Melbourne
OL,8,FCricket Ground (MCG) and the
OL,9,Fcontinuation of local Aboriginal
OL,10,Fculture is explained before the walk
OL,11,Ffinishes at the Scar Trees, a
OL,12,Fprotected cultural heritage site in
OL,13,FYarra Park.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
